			h2 В чем секрет <span>SOS-3D?</span>
			.content_box
				p Water, Tripeptide («Syn-Ake»тм), Glycerin, Palmitoyl Tripeptide–5 («Syn-Coll»тм), Acacia senegal gum (Easyliance), Petroselinum crispum (Parsley) Leaf Extract, Sodium Carbomer, Sodium Polyacrylate, Sodium Hyaluronate («Cube3»тм), DMDM hydantoin, PEG–40 Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Parfum.
